model.dataType
Class ConversationData

java.lang.Object
  model.dataType.ConversationData

public class ConversationData
extends Object

Holds all information represented in a conversation. Typically, each ConversationData object represents a new chat. When the number of or status of an object changes, the GUI should update accordingly.
